    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "s1_why",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 722,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "• the delegate PDA has no private key — only the program signs for it (invoke_signed)\n• init_session enforces  session_key ≠ owner\n• kill switch:  holder.revoke()  →  next operator.execute()  fails (SessionRevoked)",
      "originalText": "• the delegate PDA has no private key — only the program signs for it (invoke_signed)\n• init_session enforces  session_key ≠ owner\n• kill switch:  holder.revoke()  →  next operator.execute()  fails (SessionRevoked)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#475569",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
