    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "s4_alloc_t",
      "x": 140,
      "y": 2505,
      "width": 425,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Allowance mode   (SPL / Token-2022)\n──────────────────\n• funds stay in the owner's ATA\n• SPL approve → delegate PDA = TIER-1 hard cap\n• agent spends straight from the owner wallet\n• recommended for tokens",
      "originalText": "Allowance mode   (SPL / Token-2022)\n──────────────────\n• funds stay in the owner's ATA\n• SPL approve → delegate PDA = TIER-1 hard cap\n• agent spends straight from the owner wallet\n• recommended for tokens",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
